      <p>St. John's Wort has one of the deepest clinical evidence bases of any herbal supplement for mood support. A landmark <strong>Cochrane Collaboration systematic review of 29 clinical trials</strong> (5,489 participants) concluded that St. John's Wort extracts were superior to placebo and comparably effective to standard antidepressants for mild to moderate depressive symptoms, with significantly fewer side effects. Nature's Way, a company with over five decades of experience in herbal supplementation, pairs St. John's Wort with saffron extract — creating a formula that addresses mood through both monoamine reuptake inhibition and serotonergic modulation.</p>

